data.name: Desc_Complexity.Text
data.value:
Very simple These items are composed of a single piece, made of a single material, and contain no moving parts.
Very Simple items include simple weapons in the Hammer, Monk, Spear, and Thrown weapon groups, and all items made with Craft (Blacksmithing), Craft (Baskets), and Craft (Cloth).
